.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-EARNED" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-earned \- show total routing fees earned per channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-earned
.RI [ channel_id ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Aggregates settled forwards from
.B listforwards
and sums fees earned per in-channel.
Without
.IR channel_id ,
returns all channels sorted by total fee descending.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, total_fee_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1),
.BR lightning-channel-history (1)
